<item>
            <title>[LU-16142] Increase filesystem space on MGS server.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16142</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We require additional space on our MGS file-system.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lun size is currently 512GB but the file-system space only reflects 300GB available for use.&lt;br/&gt;
Is there anyway to increase the current 300GB to use all of the 512GB space on the lun and what would the procedure be?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Or do we need to inflate the lun size to 1TB and will the additional space just be available for use or what would the process be.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could not find information in the lustre operations manual.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
