                            <comment id="346187" author="JIRAUSER18408" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2022 14:55:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is it possible for us to run Lustre on rhel 8 ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If yes which version are supported.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="346159" author="adilger" created="Fri, 9 Sep 2022 10:35:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You can use &quot;resize2fs&quot; on the unmouted MGT to increase the filesystem size to match the device size. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
